{"pageProps":{"metadata":{"title":"データベース基礎","curriculumId":"1ada501e-f337-81e8-b251-df0f38a0cb23","category":"後期","visibility":["基礎班","発展班"],"tags":["基礎班","データベース","Python"],"is_basic_curriculum":true,"id":"127"},"mdBlocks":[{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-810c-a18c-ea1abd8d6021","type":"paragraph","parent":"ここではSQLで使える主なカラムの属性について列挙します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8137-92dc-ff41c608a1dc","type":"paragraph","parent":"テーブルを作成する際に参考にしてください。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-818b-aa57-fe088f10a5e8","type":"heading_2","parent":"## データ型","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-812a-a153-cf291e0d663f","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81fc-aaf9-cecdc89f3a70","type":"paragraph","parent":"**整数型**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b6-955a-d51ac5040a9e","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `INTEGER`: 整数を保存します。通常、範囲は -2,147,483,648 ～ 2,147,483,647。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8163-8f32-d0c8eaaad981","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `SMALLINT`: `INTEGER` より小さな範囲の整数（-32,768 ～ 32,767）。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8140-bcf6-f4823815699c","type":"paragraph","parent":"**浮動小数点型**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-813c-bc29-d9f21113f953","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `FLOAT`: 浮動小数点数を保存します。精度はデータベースごとに異なります。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81f1-acca-cfa4661cedff","type":"paragraph","parent":"**文字列型**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-818b-88b9-dc0e3ae4755a","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `TEXT` : 文字列型","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-818d-b0b3-eec9064e3365","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `CHAR(n)`: 固定長文字列。`n` で文字数を指定します。文字数が不足している場合、スペースで埋められます。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81d7-8bc8-f168b75f1a48","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `VARCHAR(n)`: 可変長文字列。`n` で最大文字数を指定します。文字数が不足してもスペースで埋めません。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8115-9a0b-ff98e96d2bdc","type":"paragraph","parent":"**日付と時刻**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8105-a310-e86b63f9c48e","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `DATE`: 日付を保存します（`YYYY-MM-DD` 形式）。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8123-ad6a-f79d79435f7b","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `TIME`: 時間を保存します（`HH:MM:SS` 形式）。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-812f-8fe2-d649403cdd69","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `DATETIME`: 日付と時間を合わせて保存します（`YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS` 形式）。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81d5-a9c7-f2032fd4b6b0","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `TIMESTAMP`: 日付と時間を保存し、通常は自動的に現在時刻に更新するオプションもあります。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8117-ac99-c78259b9f380","type":"paragraph","parent":"**真偽型**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8198-9061-ef42694b15cb","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `BOOLEAN`：真偽型。`0`または`1`として保存されるため、実際には`INTEGER`型として動作する。そのため注意が必要。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81bb-a65c-e4181455884d","type":"heading_2","parent":"## 制約","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-815f-a522-f6275daa8440","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-819b-a7f9-d86ef0fd98fa","type":"paragraph","parent":"**PRIMARY KEY**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b8-af37-c757a4f7f8aa","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- テーブル内で各行を一意に識別するカラムに設定します。`PRIMARY KEY` に指定されたカラムは重複を許さず、`NULL` 値も許可しません。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8138-bef1-ca91b4c38127","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-813d-804a-d8af7052fd9e","type":"paragraph","parent":"**AUTOINCREMENT**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-812f-9c09-cd0874c88500","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 主に `PRIMARY KEY` カラムに使用され、自動的に一意の連番を生成します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81df-9cef-d4b7c5366d0e","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81c3-8b5d-c97803fe6ae7","type":"paragraph","parent":"**UNIQUE**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81d3-b26d-f5f2f2d376f5","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 特定のカラムが一意であることを保証します。同じテーブル内で重複する値が入ることを防ぎます。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8139-841e-c8144c86e864","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8131-b564-d33f37074a77","type":"paragraph","parent":"**NOT NULL**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81a2-a67c-c08b75cb403c","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- `NULL` 値を禁止し、必ずデータを入力しなければならないように設定します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8125-ad01-c7f356597a41","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81a4-a87a-ee0772cba224","type":"paragraph","parent":"**CHECK**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8114-a76d-fa186b5f78a0","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- カラムに入力されるデータが特定の条件を満たすかどうかをチェックします。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8122-a341-c72d7bc5fc0f","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `age INTEGER CHECK (age >= 18)`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b1-ad05-ee4462d1a56b","type":"paragraph","parent":"**DEFAULT**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8133-b5aa-d4197657bdf2","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- カラムにデータが指定されなかった場合に、デフォルト値を自動的に設定します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8139-a30e-f0edf1ccdf44","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例：`created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-813c-a2cb-f0fbc12ff052","type":"paragraph","parent":"**FOREIGN KEY**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81db-ac9a-d9dc690b2a76","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 他のテーブルの `PRIMARY KEY` と関連付けをすることで、リレーション（外部キー制約）を作成します。参照整合性を保つために使われます。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8138-ae9b-f317d610552a","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `user_id INT, FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id)`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8167-82f8-fb4dcc9ad159","type":"paragraph","parent":"**ON DELETE CASCADE / ON UPDATE CASCADE**","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8142-8e38-cea2ca81d6e0","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 外部キーに設定し、参照元のデータが削除または更新された際に、連動して子テーブルのデータも削除または更新するようにします。","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-81b8-b3c6-c25bb797c2e6","type":"bulleted_list_item","parent":"- 例: `FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE`","children":[]},{"blockId":"1ada501e-f337-8156-a372-dd1733b6a541","type":"paragraph","parent":"","children":[]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"後期","id":"/posts/course/後期"},{"title":"データベース基礎","id":"/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81e8-b251-df0f38a0cb23/1ada501e-f337-81e8-b251-df0f38a0cb23"},{"id":"/posts/curriculums/1ada501e-f337-81e8-b251-df0f38a0cb23/1ada501e-f337-81bc-8a50-df2e526e6153","title":"カラムの属性"}],"childrenData":{"title":"データベース基礎","childPages":[{"title":"データベースとは","id":"1ada501e-f337-81ce-889f-d99449a4ba30"},{"title":"Pythonでデータベースを扱うためのライブラリ","id":"1ada501e-f337-81ea-92d1-dcb4d8f60e2a"},{"title":"データベースとの接続とテーブルの作成","id":"1ada501e-f337-8160-b03e-f28f8a18fa43"},{"title":"データの保存(Create)","id":"1ada501e-f337-8124-834c-d232ae4e3855"},{"title":"データの取得(Read)","id":"1ada501e-f337-81fe-9043-da67e48709a8"},{"title":"データの編集(Update)","id":"1ada501e-f337-815a-a9e6-d8cdd63afa9c"},{"title":"データの削除(Delete)","id":"1ada501e-f337-8190-b5d5-ff083def3250"},{"title":"テーブルの編集","id":"1ada501e-f337-81a2-bb7a-d5bc48cd5f09"},{"title":"CRUD操作を使い回せるようにしよう","id":"1ada501e-f337-81d2-8f41-cd45c5a72b38"},{"title":"マイグレーション","id":"1ada501e-f337-81ac-a7f5-efdaf65ef9e7"},{"title":"カラムの属性","id":"1ada501e-f337-81bc-8a50-df2e526e6153"},{"title":"SQL文","id":"1ada501e-f337-8175-826a-d32ae9e3e34d"}]},"pageId":"1ada501e-f337-81bc-8a50-df2e526e6153","title":"カラムの属性"},"__N_SSG":true}